OL,5, More than 100 families looking after   
OL,6, severely disabled adults and children  
OL,7, outside hospital, have told the BBC    
OL,8, that the NHS is failing to provide     
OL,9, enough vital support.                  
OL,11,FMany got in touch after a BBC report   
OL,12,Fabout a mother left on her own for long
OL,13,Fperiods to care for her son.           
OL,15,FThe NHS says help is based on          
OL,16,Findividual needs and guidelines ensure 
OL,17,Fconsistency across England and Wales.  
OL,19,FHowever, some families describe the    
OL,20,Fsystem as adversarial.                 
